name: Overexposed #0003 UFOria
description:
Overexposed collection contains generative art created by Dmitry Volodin using different algorithms but inevitably resulting in pale, pastel-like images, potentially with large white or very light areas. All drawings start with black background and are gradually filled with color, with each next layer adding to the lightness of the final piece. The artist uses Processing to create his digital paintings.

Dimensions: 3200 x 3200
